# Infinite Canvas Notes - Main Prompt

This is the main AI prompt used to generate the project.

---

## Project Goal

Build a production-ready Infinite Canvas Notes application similar to Obsidian + Miro.

---

## Requirements Provided to AI

* Infinite canvas with pan and zoom
* Drag and drop note cards
* Markdown editor with live preview
* Connections between notes with labeled edges
* Graph visualization system
* Search and filtering system
* Local-first storage using IndexedDB (no backend)
* Offline support
* Export system (Markdown, JSON, PNG, SVG)
* Responsive UI with dark/light mode

---

## Tech Stack Requested

* Next.js 15 (App Router)
* TypeScript
* Tailwind CSS
* React
* Zustand
* React Flow
* IndexedDB (Dexie)
* Service Worker (PWA support)
* Framer Motion

---

## Advanced Requirements

* Handle 500+ notes smoothly
* Handle 1000+ connections
* 60 FPS canvas performance target
* Modular architecture
* Clean component structure
* Fully offline-first design

---

## Output Expected from AI

* Full working Next.js project
* Canvas system
* Graph engine
* Markdown editor
* IndexedDB storage layer
* Export system
* PWA setup
* Tests and documentation
* Deployment configuration

---

## Constraint

* No backend allowed
* Must work fully offline
* Must be production-ready
